Class HerdAnimalsWebModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.extension.HerdAnimalsWebModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnimalTransfersWebModel, HerdFemalesWebModel, HerdMalesWebModel

    public class HerdAnimalsWebModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Auxiliary class that retrieves data of a selected group of herds which have to be displayed to a web user This class is based on class HerdAnimalsTableModel
    Author:
    patricio
